# ShadowTraffic license — TEMPLATE ONLY. This file ships with placeholder values
# that WILL NOT work. The real `license.env` is intentionally NOT in this repo:
# every operator must obtain a license first (shared team blob or an individual one).
#
# How to get real values:
#   1. Obtain a ShadowTraffic license — either the shared team `license.env` from the
#      secret store (1Password / vault / internal runbook), or your own from
#      https://shadowtraffic.io (individual trial).
#   2. Copy this file to `license.env` (gitignored) and paste in the real values,
#      OR just drop the license.env you were given in the repo root.
#   3. Run `./scripts/encode-license.sh` to copy the base64 blob to your clipboard,
#      then paste it into the Aiven Console as the SECRET env var SHADOWTRAFFIC_LICENSE.
#
# Note: LICENSE_EDITION and other values may contain spaces — do NOT add quotes.
LICENSE_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
LICENSE_EMAIL=you@example.com
LICENSE_ORGANIZATION=Your Org
LICENSE_EDITION=ShadowTraffic Free Trial
LICENSE_EXPIRATION=2099-12-31
LICENSE_SIGNATURE=REPLACE_WITH_REAL_SIGNATURE
